'''恩尼奥·莫里科内'''（{{lang-it|Ennio Morricone}}，{{bd|1928年|11月10日|2020年|7月6日|catIdx=Morricone}}）<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/06/obituaries/ennio-morricone-dead.html|title=Ennio Morricone, Influential Creator of Music for Modern Cinema, Dies at 91|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2020-06-06|accessdate=2020-07-06|archive-date=2020-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706075014/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/06/obituaries/ennio-morricone-dead.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[意大利|意大利]]作曲家，生於[[羅馬|羅馬]]，曾为超过500部的电影电视写过配乐。2007年他获得[[奥斯卡终身成就奖|奥斯卡终身成就奖]]，成为第二位获此殊荣的作曲家。他获得两次[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]，两次[[金球奖|金球奖]]，五次[[英国电影和电视艺术学院|英国电影和电视艺术学院]]奖等多项音乐奖项。2016年以《[[八惡人|八惡人]]》榮獲[[第88屆奧斯卡金像獎|第88屆奧斯卡金像獎]][[奥斯卡最佳原创音乐奖|最佳原创音乐奖]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.classicfm.com/events/oscars/news/nominations-full-list-2016/|title=Oscars 2016: composer Ennio Morricone wins his first Oscar|date=2016-02-29|work=Classic FM|access-date=2021-02-05|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116081444/https://www.classicfm.com/events/oscars/news/nominations-full-list-2016/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==生涯==
[[File:Morricone_at_United_Nations_HQ.jpg|right]]

他出生於羅馬，父母名叫Mario Morricone（職業小號手）、Libera Ridolfi（經營紡織生意）<ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=G2lqIuCFJ_MC&pg=PA1 |title=Ennio Morricone's The Good, the Bad and the Ugly: A Film Score Guide |author=Charles Leinberger |page=1 |website=Books.google.ca |date= |accessdate=6 November 2016 |archive-date=2020-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710180618/https://books.google.com/books?id=G2lqIuCFJ_MC&pg=PA1 }}</ref>，他的家庭来自[[阿尔皮诺|阿尔皮诺]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/23/Ennio-Morricone.html |title=Ennio Morricone Biography (1928–) |publisher=Filmreference.com |date= |accessdate=13 September 2011 |archive-date=2007-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071019043344/http://www.filmreference.com/film/23/Ennio-Morricone.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

他的父親是他的音樂啟蒙老師，後來他也曾進入聖塞西莉亞國立學院（Accademia Nazionale di Santa Cecilia） 學習小號，導師是Umberto Semproni。<ref>{{cite book| author = Charles Leinberger| title = Ennio Morricone's The Good, The Bad and the Ugly: A Film Score Guide| url = https://books.google.com/?id=G2lqIuCFJ_MC&pg=PA2| accessdate = 22 January 2013| date = 1 September 2004| publisher = Scarecrow Press| isbn = 978-0-8108-5132-0 }}</ref>

他著名的電影配樂作品包括《[[狂沙十萬里|狂沙十萬里]]》、《[[鏢客三部曲|鏢客三部曲]]》、《[[馬可波羅|馬可波羅]]》、《[[战火浮生|战火浮生]]》、《[[美国往事|美国往事]]》、《[[天堂电影院|天堂电影院]]》、《[[海上鋼琴師|海上鋼琴師]]》及《[[王子復仇記_(電影)|王子復仇記]]》、《[[西西里的美丽传说|西西里的美丽传说]]》等。其他创作如1978年阿根廷世界杯足球赛主题曲- "El Mundial"。

許多音樂人，如 Radiohead, Gnarls Barkley, Mike Patton, Alex Turner等，都表示他們的音樂曾受到Morricone作品的啟發。

2003年日本[[NHK|NHK]]播出的[[大河劇|大河劇]]《[[武藏MUSASHI|武藏MUSASHI]]》邀請莫里科内負責創作劇中的音樂，為第一部由外國音樂家擔當配樂工作的大河劇。

2016到2019年間，莫里科内於歐洲多個城市展開60週年紀念巡迴演出<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnso.cz/en/news/ennio-morricone-60-years-music|title=Ennio Morricone – 60 Years of Music|date=18 October 2020|publisher=Czech National Symphony Orchestra|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2022-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220227225719/https://www.cnso.cz/en/news/ennio-morricone-60-years-music}}</ref>。

2020年6月底傳出他本人在家中跌倒摔傷、送醫住院接受治療的消息，但於7月6日經證實因傷勢導致併發症而過世，享壽91歲<ref>{{Cite web |title=Morto Ennio Morricone, aveva 91 anni: fatale una caduta, si era rotto il femore |url=https://www.ilmessaggero.it/spettacoli/musica/ennio_morricone_morto_roma_oggi_6_luglio_2020_musica_c_era_una_volta_in_america-5330102.html |access-date=6 July 2020 |website=www.ilmessaggero.it |date=6 July 2020 |language=it |archive-date=2020-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706124026/https://www.ilmessaggero.it/spettacoli/musica/ennio_morricone_morto_roma_oggi_6_luglio_2020_musica_c_era_una_volta_in_america-5330102.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=McFadden |first=Robert D. |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/06/obituaries/ennio-morricone-dead.html |title=Ennio Morricone, Influential Creator of Music for Modern Cinema, Dies at 91 |newspaper=The New York Times |date=6 July 2020 |access-date=6 July 2020 |archive-date=2020-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706075014/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/06/obituaries/ennio-morricone-dead.html }}</ref>。

== 合作艺术家 ==
华裔大提琴演奏家[[馬友友|馬友友]]曾與莫里科内合作，改編部份电影电视精選配乐成為大提琴演奏曲，在2004年由[[新力古典|新力古典]]發行專輯唱片《{{tsl|en|Yo-Yo Ma Plays Ennio Morricone||Yo-Yo Ma Plays Ennio Morricone}}》，曲目包括：《[[战火浮生|战火浮生]]》、《[[海上鋼琴師|海上鋼琴師]]》、《{{tsl|en|A_Pure_Formality||A Pure Formality}}》、《[[新天堂樂園|新天堂樂園]]》、《[[美国往事|美国往事]]》、《[[狂沙十萬里|狂沙十萬里]]》、《[[黃昏三鑣客|黃昏三鑣客]]》、《{{tsl|en|Casualties_of_War|孽戰|Casualties of War}}》、《[[铁面无私|義膽雄心]]》、《{{tsl|en|Moses_the_Lawgiver||Moses}}》、《[[马可波罗_(电视短剧)|馬可勃羅]]》、《{{tsl|en|La_califfa||The Lady Caliph}}》等樂曲，受到[[美联社|美联社]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.boston.com/ae/specials/2004_best_of/articles/ap_writers_top_10_albums_of_the_year/ |title=2004 AP Honorable Mentions albums |access-date=2009-06-02 |archive-date=2006-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060714034324/http://www.boston.com/ae/specials/2004_best_of/articles/ap_writers_top_10_albums_of_the_year/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>及 [[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.amazon.com/Yo-Yo-Ma-Plays-Ennio-Morricone/product-reviews/B0002YCVXI/ref=dp_top_cm_cr_acr_img?ie=UTF8&showViewpoints=1 |title=亞馬遜公司用戶評鑒 |access-date=2009-06-02 |archive-date=2020-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916024716/https://www.amazon.com/Yo-Yo-Ma-Plays-Ennio-Morricone/product-reviews/B0002YCVXI/ref=dp_top_cm_cr_acr_img?ie=UTF8&showViewpoints=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>用戶的好評。

2010年，恩尼奥·莫里科内在[[意大利|意大利]][[罗马|罗马]]与[[新西兰|新西兰]]古典[[跨界音乐|跨界音乐]][[女高音|女高音]][[海莉·薇思特拉|海莉·薇思特拉]]合作了一张新的国际专辑《[[天堂之音|天堂之音]]》，于2011年4月18日自新西兰开始向全球发布此专辑。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.marbecks.co.nz/detail/index.lsd?catalogID=621881 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2011-04-17 |archive-date=2011-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110929202933/http://www.marbecks.co.nz/detail/index.lsd?catalogID=621881 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/hqgj/jryw/2011-09-28/content_3924021.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2011-10-07 |archive-date=2017-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707132422/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/hqgj/jryw/2011-09-28/content_3924021.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>恩尼奥·莫里科内不仅为此专辑谱写新歌和他的成名作品，还安排他在罗马的管弦乐队为此专辑配乐。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.decca.com/articles/hayley-westenra-teams-up-with-ennio-morricone-490 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-03-08  |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120102101232/http://www.decca.com/articles/hayley-westenra-teams-up-with-ennio-morricone-490 |archivedate=2012-01-02 }}</ref>

